              </content>
            </subparagraph>
          </subparagraph>
          <subparagraph>
            <num><span style="color:#4F81BD">•</span></num>
            <intro>
              <p><span style="color:#000000">The Social Security Contributions (Disregarded Payments) (Coronavirus) (Scotland and Wales) Regulations 2020 (S.I. 2020/1532).</span></p>
            </intro>
